---
Source:
  Title: A Year with Rumi
  Translator: Coleman Barks
  Author: Rumi
  ISBN: 978-0060845971
  Publisher: HarperOne
Format: Verse
By: Rumi
Title: Blessing
Description: April 6
---
I want to be where
your bare foot walks,

because maybe before you step,
you will look at the ground.
I want that blessing.
